{"tid":2374590,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企令你唔相信愛情圍爐區","createTime":"2021-01-21T10:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:13:30.000Z","uid":186374,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"720f53bc94ef5181b57ae752c5b2e8db613ef163","tid":2374590,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"講下自己<br />\n家母全職主婦<br />\n家父由結婚開始一路出軌幾十年嚟都係咁<br />\n單身女人 女同事 女客人 已婚人妻<br />\n應有盡有<br />\n雖然據我所知冇私生子<br />\n因為家父係真。自私 偷食完即飛 會比錢人落仔<br />\n<br />\n家母當初為咗頭家冇離婚<br />\n佢話真係好唔想自己小朋友（即係我同我家姐）係單親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾廢老發現除咗自己糟糠之妻之外<br />\n根本冇女人會留喺佢身邊照顧佢<br />\n就「醒悟」咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家對家母好好<br />\n但係家母對家父只係得返恨意<br />\n所以有時會發佢脾氣<br />\n但係衣食上仍然照顧得佢好好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解我家姐冇太受屋企影響<br />\n仍然可以自然咁拍拖 結婚<br />\n仲幾美滿<br />\n但係我就完全有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以分享下自己係點克服"},{"pid":"51578d9018f350174f0af53ffc7fafa74a07f54d","tid":2374590,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"洗鬼上黎開post<br />\n問你家姐"},{"pid":"b9628e2a02d7c96c1b05ceab6143f1d09796f502","tid":2374590,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51578d9018f350174f0af53ffc7fafa74a07f54d","tid":2374590,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"洗鬼上黎開post<br />\n問你家姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死開"},{"pid":"ddea35b1001988e21a5d90b545e95350bd4977fe","tid":2374590,"uid":345784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51578d9018f350174f0af53ffc7fafa74a07f54d","tid":2374590,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"洗鬼上黎開post<br />\n問你家姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f3141b7ae99742be2f0edb1c02df30a6100124","tid":2374590,"uid":390050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}